eu.wauz.wauzcore.skills.skillgems

Class SkillWheelOfFortune

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.wauz.wauzcore.skills.skillgems.SkillWheelOfFortune
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WauzPlayerSkill

    public class SkillWheelOfFortune
extends java.lang.Object
implements WauzPlayerSkill
    A skill, that can be executed by a player. "Random" casts a random skill, while the cooldown and mana cost stays the same, independant of the skill's own values.
    Author:
    Wauzmons
